 var list = new List<int>();
 list.EnsureCapacity(10000);
 for (int i = 0; i < 10000; i++)
     list.Add(i);
 ```

 **Impact: Reduces reallocations and array copies during bulk operations.**

 ### Use TryGetNonEnumeratedCount for Pre-Sizing
